  "text": "Following the Lyapunov optimization approach, we add the expected energy consumption with > 0 over units (i.e., a penalty function), E{ ( )}, to (7), which leads to the driftplus-penalty term. This is a key step to obtain an upper bound on this term. Before further discussing the drift-plus-penalty term, we first present a lemma in [CITATION_1] , which is related to the derivation of the upper bound of drift-plus-penalty term.",
